                                "stop": 10.002,
                                "byte_start": 89595,
                                "byte_stop": 129615,
                                "text": "The Opinion of the Court in No. 99-2036 Good New Club versus Milford Central School will be announced by Justice Thomas."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 10.002,
                        "stop": 188.995,
